beer.beer_description:
Golden Ale is a style that has a beaut balance of Ale and Crystal malts and is hopped using Goldings and Pride of Ringwood for a bit of nostalgic Aussie bitterness and Willamette and Cascade for a more modern aroma driven style. Gold is crisp and fresh with earthy malt flavours, a soft mouth feel and a satisfying fruity finish as dry as summer is long.

Golden Ale is our homage to the rough cut blokes and sheilas who got the rush and the fever dragging great hunks of glorious gold out of the creeks and gullies around sunny Central Victoria.

A great session beer, equally at home at a backyard bbq, over your favourite bar or sharing a feed with family and friends.
